<item chapterid="609770" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1951" articlename="惹火甜妻：总裁撩上瘾" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521893546" lastupdate="1521893546" chaptername="第28章看来运气还真不错" chapterorder="28" size="4141" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    想着想着，凌瑶瑶就情不自禁扬起了嘴角，露出了开心甜美的笑意。

